room_title: Escape room "White House Down" by Race to Escape in Tampa
room_address: 2435 US Highway 19 N Suite 101 Holiday, FL 34691
room_description: A terrorist organization in opposition to the United States has acquired a nuclear missile. The terrorists have infiltrated the White House and plan to launch a nuclear strike against the United States. You are the only remaining group in the White House that is tasked to activate the missile defense system against the incoming nuclear strike. Succeed in order for millions to survive. Failure is not an option.
